{"body": "It's valid for the massive community still on 3.0 and represents a fairly annoying bug.  Close it if 3.0 is not accepting any bug fixes.\n\nHere's my monkey patch:\n```ruby\nmodule ActionView\n  module Helpers\n    private\n\n    def is_uri_with_agnostic?(path)\n      path =~ %r{^\\/\\/} || is_uri_without_agnostic?(path)\n    end\n    alias_method_chain :is_uri?, :agnostic\n  end\nend\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6111743", "created_at": "2012-06-04T21:35:01Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6625#issuecomment-6111743", "updated_at": "2012-06-04T21:35:01Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6625, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/kylev", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/ee075c7c5bdcad2baed4915630fe9a39?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F107fce5988735e531cae0da812db9a62.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/received_events", "gravatar_id": "ee075c7c5bdcad2baed4915630fe9a39", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "kylev", "type": "User", "id": 46888, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kylev/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52380625bd3543c15100c878"}, "id": 6111743, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6625"}
